      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解起点是TrackingNumber，然后流向DeliveryRoute，再到FleetManagement。这三个节点用顺序箭头连接对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
