    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果是的话，先经过FleetManagement中转，然后回到TrackingNumber更新状态，最后再进入FleetManagement结束这个分支。",
